   <p begin="00:20:25.475" end="00:20:28.102" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャ〜</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:20:28.186" end="00:20:30.480" style="s1"><span style="s2">リマ… リマ…</span></p> 
